sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    %% Flow 1: InferenceService Model Serving (Raw Deployment Mode)
    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
    Note over Client,CloudStorage: Flow 1: InferenceService — Raw Deployment Mode
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Gateway / Ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant PredSvc as {isvc}-predictor Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP or 8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant CloudStorage as Cloud Storage<br/>(S3 / GCS / Azure / HF / OCI)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Client->>Gateway: HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: None or OAuth
    Gateway->>PredSvc: HTTPRoute → Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP or 8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: None or kube-rbac-proxy
    PredSvc->>Predictor: HTTP/8080<br/>No encryption
    Note over Predictor,CloudStorage: Init container (storage-initializer) runs first
    Predictor->>CloudStorage: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Cloud credentials (IAM/JSON/Token)
    CloudStorage-->>Predictor: Model artifacts
    Predictor-->>PredSvc: Inference result
    PredSvc-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response
    end

    %% Flow 2: LLMInferenceService with Scheduler (Gateway API)
    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
    Note over Client,Prometheus: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService — Gateway API + Scheduler
    participant PlatformGW as Platform Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant InfPool as InferencePool<br/>(scheduler routing)
    participant EPP as Scheduler EPP<br/>9002/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant WorkloadPod as Workload Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>HTTPS TLS
    participant WVA as WVA Autoscaler

    Client->>PlatformGW: HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Kuadrant AuthPolicy
    PlatformGW->>InfPool: HTTPRoute → InferencePool
    InfPool->>EPP: gRPC/9002<br/>TLS (self-signed)<br/>Auth: None
    EPP->>WorkloadPod: HTTPS/8000<br/>TLS (self-signed or service-ca)<br/>Auth: None
    WorkloadPod-->>EPP: Inference result
    EPP-->>InfPool: Response
    InfPool-->>PlatformGW: Response
    PlatformGW-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over WVA,Prometheus: Autoscaling feedback loop
    WVA->>Prometheus: Query wva_desired_replicas<br/>HTTPS / Bearer Token
    Prometheus-->>WVA: Metric values
    WVA->>WorkloadPod: Scale via HPA/KEDA
    end

    %% Flow 3: InferenceGraph Routing
    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
    Note over Client,ISvcB: Flow 3: InferenceGraph — Multi-model Routing
    participant RouterSvc as Router Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant ISvcA as InferenceService A<br/>(predictor)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant ISvcB as InferenceService B<br/>(transformer)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Client->>RouterSvc: HTTP/8080<br/>Auth: None
    RouterSvc->>ISvcA: HTTP/8080 — Step node
    ISvcA-->>RouterSvc: Partial result
    RouterSvc->>ISvcB: HTTP/8080 — Step node
    ISvcB-->>RouterSvc: Partial result
    RouterSvc-->>Client: Combined response
    end
